    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2008-09-25</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2008-10-31T19:40:46Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Safeguarding Our Hospitals' Futures Act of 2008 - Requires the Secretary of Health and Human Services, in the case of discharges occurring on or after October 1, 2008, to continue to apply budget neutrality on a national basis in the calculation of the urban hospital wage floor for discharges occurring during FY2008 under title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act (through a uniform, national adjustment to the area wage index).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
